I have a solid picture of the project. Here's my hypothesis before asking questions:

**Alea** is a member management platform for a cultural gaming association — members reserve tables in 6 Tolkien-themed rooms to play tabletop RPGs and board games. The platform handles reservations, QR-based check-ins, and admin management. MVP is days away (April 14).

